      <section>
      <h3>MOTIVATIONS</h3>
      <li>We can contribute by actively participating in class discussions, sharing ideas during group work,
      and helping classmates when they need support. We will also show respect to teachers and peers and do our tasks responsibly.</li>
      </section>
      </ul>
      <br>
      
